<item>
            <title>[LU-3352] conf-sanity test_73: failover nids haven&apos;t changed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3352</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e5d0ffde-bd82-11e2-a548-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e5d0ffde-bd82-11e2-a548-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_73 failed with the following error in the test output:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;failover nids haven&apos;t changed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 73&lt;/p&gt;</description>
