                            <comment id="60013" author="emoly.liu" created="Wed, 5 Jun 2013 07:25:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/6550&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/6550&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="60012" author="emoly.liu" created="Wed, 5 Jun 2013 06:52:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This problem is probably caused by the script&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;do_facet ost1 &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$TUNEFS --failnode=1.2.3.4@tcp $(ostdevname 1)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;removing &quot;@tcp&quot; should work on IB network.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59854" author="emoly.liu" created="Mon, 3 Jun 2013 08:29:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The maloo search result showed that conf-sanity test_73 had never passed with networktype=o2ib since it was created.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
